{
  "stem": "16792.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And maybe today, it is the same.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe after 100 years, [INAUDIBLE] is different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But this is the way it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Uh, normally, we-- what we was doing was we was going every Saturday to schul, and with all the family-- maybe it was old already, or young, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we was-- and members from our schul, from also from our family, they're calling it the [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shankus Stevel. ?] And the name-- the name was [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Shankus. ?] And he give-- the whole building, he give for these people, which did for the congregation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He give it free, away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't charge anything for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And down there, we-- we was going Friday night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we was going Saturday morning to schul, to pray.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we came back, and then we come home, so we talking about Friday night and Saturday.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But Friday night-- normally, it was like a holiday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Every Friday night and Saturday was like a holiday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The reason was we are not people which-- when I was young, which drink a lot of alcohol.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But my mother used to do, she prepared Thursday-- um, Thursday, the grapes-- the grapes from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she put a little bit sugar, and she put it away in a warm side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this, Friday night, she drain it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we was drinking this for kiddush like wine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this is the way it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then we-- we baked challah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Every Thursday, my mother baked challah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, uh-- we have got-- by the dinner, we have got-- always, we got two kind of fish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We got gefilte fish and carp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "After that, we got soup with all kinds of different items in it-- different items.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
